NAME
	get_dir - Retreive information about the  contents of a directory.
		
SYNOPSIS
	static mixed **get_dir(string dir)

DESCRIPTION
	Get_dir returns 3 arrays, file names, filesizes, filemod times.
	Directories have a file size of -2.  If no file or directory exists
	the return value will be three empty arrays ({ ({ }), ({ }), ({ }) })
		
RETURN VALUE
	Returns 1 on success and 0 on failure.

